column.name: Query
column.value: "SELECT TOP 1 CASE WHEN RAND() < 0.5 THEN 'NonMemberCustomer' ELSE T_TIERS END AS T_TIERS, T_REGIMETVA FROM dbo.TIERS WHERE T_NATUREAUXI = 'CLI' AND (ABS(CAST( (BINARY_CHECKSUM(*) * RAND()) as int)) % 100) < 10 AND T_NATUREAUXI = 'CLI' and T_Tiers not in ( 'INVENT', 'NonMemberCustomer', 'PASSANT', 'PASSANTB', 'SPECBEW', 'TRANSFER' ) AND T_REGIMETVA = 'NL' UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 CASE WHEN RAND() < 0.5 THEN 'NonMemberCustomer' ELSE T_TIERS END AS T_TIERS, T_REGIMETVA FROM dbo.TIERS WHERE T_NATUREAUXI = 'CLI' AND (ABS(CAST( (BINARY_CHECKSUM(*) * RAND()) as int)) % 100) < 10 AND T_NATUREAUXI = 'CLI' and T_Tiers not in ( 'INVENT', 'NonMemberCustomer', 'PASSANT', 'PASSANTB', 'SPECBEW', 'TRANSFER' ) AND T_REGIMETVA = 'BE' UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 CASE WHEN RAND() < 0.5 THEN 'NonMemberCustomer' ELSE T_TIERS END AS T_TIERS, T_REGIMETVA FROM dbo.TIERS WHERE T_NATUREAUXI = 'CLI' AND (ABS(CAST( (BINARY_CHECKSUM(*) * RAND()) as int)) % 100) < 10 AND T_NATUREAUXI = 'CLI' and T_Tiers not in ( 'INVENT', 'NonMemberCustomer', 'PASSANT', 'PASSANTB', 'SPECBEW', 'TRANSFER' ) AND T_REGIMETVA = 'UK'"
